          <from>MR. GORDIE GOSSE</from>
          <p>MR. GORDIE GOSSE : Mr. Speaker, my question through you is to the Premier. As every member of this House knows, the closure of the Veterans Affairs office in Sydney has made life very difficult for our veterans. The NDP believes our veterans stood up for us when we needed them the most, and now it's our turn to stand up for them.</p>
