          <p>HON. PAT DUNN : Madam Speaker, Roots for Youth provides crucial supports for young people struggling with homelessness in northern Nova Scotia. Since their official opening in 2011, they have helped hundreds of young people by giving them a safe place to stay and providing the necessary support services. In March 2014 alone, they have assisted well into the hundreds of young people with a variety of issues.</p>
