        <speech by="#40342c81-d15f-4412-9e39-be7ba9a478a9">
          <from>HON. MAUREEN MACDONALD</from>
          <p>HON. MAUREEN MACDONALD : Madam Speaker, I'm rising on the supposed point of order to essentially say that in my view that was not a point of order. We have a disagreement between members about a set of facts. With respect to what was unparliamentary, that also, I think, is not substantiated by what generally would be seen as being not parliamentary.</p>
        </speech>
